embeds.title: Welcome to "FrontWing's ISLAND"!
embeds.description:
Welcome to Urashima, the home and place where ISLAND takes place. This is one of the newest Discord servers, revolving around the Visual Novel, Anime and Manga "ISLAND".

This server is a place for all ISLAND fans, future fans and other people who are just looking for a chill and relaxing server. We offer a welcoming, comfy and small community and several other options for you to pass time!

For all who are not interested in any server activities, we have some premium and unique emotes for all the Nitro users to make use of. All of them are only available in this server and are exclusive!

embeds.title: Rules that you have to follow:
embeds.description:
➜ No racism, bullying, discrimination or anything similar.
➜ No NSFW content of any kind.
➜ No flirting, dating or overly sexual conversations.

➜ No excessive pinging or spamming.
➜ No advertisement in chat or DMs.
➜ No extremely offensive phrases.

➜ No controversial topics in chat.
➜ Don't share any illegal content.
➜ Don't try to find or abuse loopholes.

➜ Exclusively use English.
➜ Post content in the right channels.
➜ Follow Discord's Terms of Services.

Discord ToS: https://discord.com/terms
Guidelines: https://discord.com/guidelines

Breaking any of the rules can and will lead to actions being taken depending on the rule. We try to have a welcoming and peaceful atmosphere, please treat everyone well and with respect.

embeds.title: Server Boosters
embeds.description:
Boosts will help the server gain more emote slots and server-wide features, such as a server banner, higher stream quality, higher upload rate or even a custom invite link for the entire server. Boosts are highly appreciated but are voluntary.

All boosters have the option to get a custom role. Just write a message, with your desired role name as well as the hex code for the color. This website can assist you in selecting a color: https://htmlcolorcodes.com/

**Example:** "Ohara Rinne" #00ffcc
